I'm in a high seat waiting for a buck to show up

00:00:24.597 --> 00:00:31.597
Testing waterproofness of my gear ;)

00:00:41.682 --> 00:00:48.682
Face and hands covered because of midges...

00:00:57.679 --> 00:01:04.679
I have to be quick, deer don't give much time for a shot here 

