I like to examine the place where deer stood 
 even if I know where it dropped

00:02:04.130 --> 00:02:11.130
It makes sense to collect hair for future reference...

00:02:20.258 --> 00:02:27.260
Nice 5-pointer

00:02:28.951 --> 00:02:36.950
Probably only 2-3 yo, but on this ground all bucks get shot

